{"tid":801850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句「帶我食飯就好」 紅透大陸四川妺 原來是做....","createTime":"2018-09-01T03:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T07:29:39.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"be33395ad47c911e1f49a962f911d4d464c05d02","tid":801850,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:54:39.000Z","msg":"「想搵個肯同自己挨麥記嘅女人」，曾是不少未婚港男的心聲！但一餐飯就能夠滿足的女友，會不會更加吸引？四川成都市早前有「抖音」用家，在街頭與一名長髮靚女做訪問：「你覺得男人一個月多少工資可以養活你？」長髮靚女甜笑着神回一句：「養活我啊？我覺得能帶我吃飯就好」，令她極速爆紅，獲封「成都小甜甜」，不但有逾500萬粉絲跟隨，當地商家更乘勢抽水，使她迅速成為四川曝光率最高的廣告模特兒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180901/58629057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180901%2F58629057&d=rPgQoPP2bU%2BhQE9jxV%2FwA26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=74ac08c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180901%2F58629057&h=13751caf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180901/58629057</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180901/large/1535764538_ee2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180901%2Flarge%2F1535764538_ee2e.jpg&h=399587bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真相<br />\n<br />\n該網民在抖音上發佈一段名為「這就是你們的女神小甜甜」的影片，稱當日街訪表示想要平凡生活的小甜甜，竟坐上一輛疑似黃色林寶堅尼的跑車，當她發現有人拍攝，仍露出招牌甜笑，然後害羞遮臉。跑車內的男司機，卻不耐煩地揮手說「滾滾滾」。<br />\n<br />\n影片流傳不久就被刪除。有網民看後感嘆留言：「她只是說了男人都愛聽得話，用女人的話說，就是甜言蜜語」、「滾滾滾，屌絲韭菜就別幻想了」、「姑娘不傻，坐在跑車裏面吃飯，不虧」。不過，也有網友指，沒證據證明影片中的女主角就是成都小甜甜，便懷疑是否有人惡意抹黑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180901/58630152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180901%2F58630152&d=rPgQoPP2bU%2BhQE9jxV%2FwA26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=8ea8c268\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180901%2F58630152&h=b6c57a75\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180901/58630152</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男人好多性幻想"},{"pid":"98d91b15b6cd872b0eb938c181aaca08ab8e3e73","tid":801850,"uid":53672,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:55:50.000Z","msg":"呢d大陸樣一睇就知啦"},{"pid":"3fad4c11b2c9666c64cb53a6e20e8bdc2e616958","tid":801850,"uid":27802,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:56:54.000Z","msg":"佢冇錯喎 帶佢食飯<br />\n人地餐餐要魚翅鮑魚咋嘛<br />\n你估同你街邊食腸粉啊？"},{"pid":"df4e983cb69574e2343ce79a7dc920474eb3de5b","tid":801850,"uid":61280,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:07:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">拆字：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">女支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"93069a9ce645c4f577ba368abebe1dbb7d954ad0","tid":801850,"uid":66943,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1HRf17M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1HRf17M.gif&h=355a820d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5cca56336418e4c2a0cb5ece7fefc9895256451","tid":801850,"uid":26752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"df4e983cb69574e2343ce79a7dc920474eb3de5b","tid":801850,"uid":61280,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:07:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">拆字：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">女支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span>